<varlistentry id="options.AutoReverse">
	<term>AutoReverse <emphasis remap='I'>0|1|2</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Specifies the window Warping (also called alt-tabbing) style.  0
		(the  default)  causes switching among windows in one direction.
		1  causes  a  closed  loop  switching  -   #1->#2->#3->#4   then
		#4->#3->#2->#1. 2 causes an open loop switching - #1->#2->#3->#4
		then #4->#1->#2->#3 etc.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
